<div class="about-content">
	<div class="about-text">
		<div class="about-text-title">
			<h1>I make shapes appear on the web.</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="about-text-body">
			<p>Hey there! I'm Daniel - I'm a school-taught Software Engineer with a B.S. in Computer Science, and I am a self-taught web developer currently working as a Software Engineer and Dev Lead on the CX team at FloSports. So, I suppose to say <span style="color: #2b60ff;">"I make shapes appear on the web"</span> is an oversimplification of what I do, but it does make for a great tagline. I am very passionate about doing things the "right" way, and on every project I work on, I always strive to perfect my efficiency and productivity as a coder while also getting even the smallest details <em style="color: #2b60ff">just</em> right.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<img class="headshot" src="./assets/headshot.png" alt="Headshot of Daniel Holthus">
</div>

<style lang="scss">
	.about-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column-reverse;
		align-items: center;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.about-text {
		margin-top: -30px;
	}

	.about-text-title {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		border: 1px solid #222222;
		padding: 12px 30px;
		background-color: #2b60ff;
		border-radius: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		h1 {
			color: var(--gray-900);
			font-size: 8vw;
		}
	}

	.about-text-body {
		padding: 0 1rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.headshot {
		width: 75%;
		border: 2px solid #222222;
		border-radius: 20px;
		background-color: #e9e1dc;
	}

	/* Desktop styles */
	@media (min-width: 54em) {

		.about-text-title {
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			border: 1px solid #222222;
			padding: 12px 30px;
			background-color: #2b60ff;
			border-radius: 20px;
			text-align: start;
			h1 {
				color: var(--gray-900);
				font-size: 4vw;
			}
		}
		
		.about-content {
			flex-direction: row;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.about-text {
			position: relative;
			z-index: 2;
			transform: translate(30px, 12px);
			width: 50%;
		}

		.about-text-body {
			padding: 0 5rem 0 2rem;
			font-size: max(1.1rem, 1.5dvw);
		}

